room_title: Escape room "Baby Gangster" by That Escape Room in San Francisco
room_description: The principal of Flower Baby Kindergarten Ben McAllister is also an assassin for the mafia. Police don't have a search warrant for him. You guys are some 9 to 10-year-old CIA trained super babies. This is your first task. You have to find your way to the principal's office and find the client list for the evidence.
